data.description: Adorable 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath colonial nestled on scenic, wooded lot on a cul-de-sac! This charming 2,672 square ft of living space offers an abundance of natural light and an open floor plan. Step inside onto the wood-look ceramic foyer. French doors open to your bright and spacious office. The two-story great room features a gas fireplace with mirrored accent wall and a whole wall of windows. The updated eat-in kitchen includes granite counters, glass tile backsplash, new lights over the table and island area (2023) and wood-look ceramic tile floor. Half bath and laundry room complete the first floor! Slider from the kitchen leads outside to the private, fenced yard with huge composite deck and shed! Upstairs, the spacious owners suite has a vaulted ceiling, wall of windows overlooking the backyard, walk-in closet and updated ensuite bath with dual vessel sinks and a custom step-in shower with beautiful tile! 2 large bedrooms and another full bath complete the second level. The full lower level offers a finished rec room with built-in cabinets, extra storage area and is plumbed for another full bath. Recent updates include roof and water heater(2021), garage door and radon system (2020)!
